Text.val: Cache on TABELGEGEVENS:

SQL_STMT_U.val: select t.tb_symbool from tabelgegevens t, toegelordercontrole c where t.tb_soort = 'ORDR' and t.tb_nummer <= 5 and c.toc_ordertraject = ~1 and c.toc_ordertype = 'B' and c.toc_marktmodel = ~2 and c.toc_geldigheid = t.tb_symbool order by t.tb_nummer desc
